title: >>> I 17 (Continued)
body_text:
Find out what the rest of the world thinks of
2005 vs. 2007
...
"I think Adams vs. Cornero will be a great matchup and really tells to the talent level that the up and coming stars have ..."
- DAN TURNER
"These two young stars have made such an impact on the game, Kevin since Season 1 and Grant since Season 8. They are both young blood that are cheered and feared on the court. Any time they step out and face each other it's sure to be a great match, and a captains battle seems to be the perfect stage for an epic battle."
- SARA DECUIR
"… a great clash of very agile and athletic, 2005 vs. 2007, dodgeball players."
- DIANA DIBUCCIO
